sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as "Client Application"
    participant API as "REST API"
    participant DB as "Database"
    Note over Client,API: REST API Request
    Client->>API: Send HTTP Request
    API->>API: Validate Request
    API->>DB: Query Database
    DB->>API: Return Data
    API->>API: Process Data
    API->>Client: Return HTTP Response
    Note over Client,API: Response Received
    Client->>Client: Parse Response
    Client->>Client: Update Application State